        "created_at": "2020-05-11T02:04:29.211Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Thanks.<br>\nI tried to restore using this backup and the current state is: only the node executing fdbrestore has a full backup, other nodes only have part of the backup and then the restore succeeds. Does this mean that every backup_agent does not necessarily need a full backup?</p>",
